title: Episode 17: K Camp
itunes:title: Episode 17: K Camp
description:
K Camp slid through Lip Service with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago, Leah MOB and Sasha DelValle right before his album release and got comfortable with the ladies. He talked about crunchy masturbation towels, saving cats, and sex waivers. Make sure you interpret his answer to whether or not he's in a relationship!
